sourcesContent: import{blue as o,purple as r,green as p,yellow as x,red as e,cyan as a,pink as g,gray as t}from"./colors";export default{colors:{background:"$white",foreground:"$black",backgroundContrast:"$white",...o,...r,...p,...x,...e,...a,...g,...t,text:"$gray900",link:"$blue600",codeLight:"$pink100",code:"$pink600",selection:"$blue200"},shadows:{xs:"-4px 0 4px rgb(0 0 0 / 5%);",sm:"0 5px 20px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)",md:"0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15)",lg:"0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15)",xl:"0 40px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25)"}};
